Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,February 28. Weather, clear.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.62,0:00:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, after thinking about it for a while,\NI made a confession.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.21,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami. Kagami?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawn... What is it? I'm busy.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.58,0:00:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, umm, actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.33,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami... Be my friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to sleep! I'm being serious!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.42,0:01:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawn... It just sounds extremely complicated\Nso I'd rather not get involved.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.08,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! You know I came to this school\Nin the middle of the semester, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.46,0:01:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, I'm the younger sister\Nof my own homeroom teacher,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.38,0:01:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which immediately gives the\Nimpression that something's up.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that my idiot brother said...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.12,0:01:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sasami has been a hikikomori for a long time.\NI feel sorry for her."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.92,0:01:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...making it sound like I've got a terrible past.\NNow everyone's keeping their distance from me!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then they're just watching me from afar,\Nacting like I'm some kind of fragile object.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.62,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And whenever they talk to me, they sound so formal.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.62,0:01:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but they sound like\Nthey're talking to a much older person, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.83,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're right. I'm sorry that I didn't realize that.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.17,0:01:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing it too!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.12,0:01:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I just want to have a normal school life!\NNormal and ordinary!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.96,0:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only have a little over one month left\Nfor my first year in high school!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.25,0:02:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't understand\Nwhy you'd want to be my friend now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.67,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that I should be friends with someone\Nlike you first and establish friendship,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.04,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually change others' perceptions\Nabout me as a cheerful and smiley girl,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.42,0:02:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they could feel comfortable talking to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.75,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the part "someone like you"\Ndoesn't sit well with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.42,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I've never had a friend before,\Nso I have no idea what to do at a time like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.67,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so Kagami...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...basically I want to use you as a demo!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.62,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're already aware of my background\NI don't have to worry too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be perfect for practice.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, as an "in-between" friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.71,0:02:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what kind of disturbing statement\Nyou're making as a human being?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawn.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.88,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.92,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First, as my friend, I want you to be\Nconsiderate of my feelings and let me sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! We're friends, right? Okay. Good night!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too loud. Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.92,0:03:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And just like that, I had a new friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.00,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lunchtime. Class is over, so wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, already?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat lunch together!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because we're friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.17,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can survive without eating.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.46,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to take a nice nap during lunch,\Nthe one time you're actually allowed to do so.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're sleeping even when you're NOT allowed, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to look unnatural\Nif friends don't eat lunch together!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.21,0:05:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm going to put our desks together,\Nso you can go ahead and eat. I'll sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to look even more unnatural!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring lunch today. Let's go to the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you're annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.83,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'll go with you since we're friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.83,0:05:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Tsukuyomi! You're our only hope!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have some more?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't lose! We won't lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that little kid teacher a monster or what?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.54,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My Big Sis is in there, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he died.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Big Sis?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see we're having an eating battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're supposed to pay for all my cafeteria bills if I win.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you wager?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A smooch on the cheek!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.25,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigh.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.17,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, men are hopelessly simple and stupid...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to apologize. It was an accident.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.12,0:06:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sasami, but I'm going to change.\NYou go ahead and have lunch alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.38,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're friends, let's go do something\Ninstead of just sleeping all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Be friends with me all you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a nap in the meantime.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami, let's go to the restroom together!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.38,0:07:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.29,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you still can't go to the restroom alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.00,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it! I've always wanted to go to\Nthe restroom hand in hand with my friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're girls, and that's what we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a robot; I have no business in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.75,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that! You can wait for me outside, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going in there with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.96,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami... We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.08,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the point of this whatsoever.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.88,0:07:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. At the very least,\NI'm letting them know that I've got a friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I sign up for this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I stepped on something.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.25,0:08:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder the pressure points on\Nthe sole of my foot were being stimulated.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.58,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. I'm not human, so pressure like this wouldn't-
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-hurt me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.08,0:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the rotation of the stars\Nisn't very smooth today.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go empty your bowels alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how Kagami and I became friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I want the salmon next.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.62,0:08:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami's always sleeping, but she's got good grades.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want just half of that rice.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She can memorize anything in the textbooks by sight.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no problem doing 7-digit math in her head.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.21,0:09:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate wasabi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.92,0:09:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NI hate wasabi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's on a high level.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll ask her to help me with studying.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you if you let the rice touch the soy sauce.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "ah"!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.25,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami was a robot with no will at the beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.25,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NTea.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.96,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An evil organization designed her, using\Na fragment of Tsurugi, but she kidnapped her.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotions started to grow inside her\Nas she spent more time with Tsurugi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.67,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if her incomplete emotions are the reason\Nwhy Kagami seems cold sometimes, or...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasami...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.38,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you talk only about Kagami?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.50,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ever make any comment\Nor tweet about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.25,0:09:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasami, please... please... please!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please eat me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who can love you the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop putting sushi on your nipple!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.33,0:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you embarrass me in public like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll do that at home next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.46,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you do that at home either!\NI mean, don't let there be a next time!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do with you, Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.04,0:10:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sasami?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.79,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kagami? What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you two... On the way home?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop mumbling nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.96,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go to the hospital right away!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.00,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you guys, I'm built tough.\NI'll recover before you know it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just taking a nap.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've come talk to me! We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.17,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please keep that "friends" stuff only in school?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.71,0:11:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For the record, you're only using me as a demo\Nin order to make friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.42,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of idea you have,\Nbut your clinginess is annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Kagami... Kagami...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawn... What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.08,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I got some free movie tickets,\Nso do you want to come?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.46,0:12:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I already have plans for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you available?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go hang out? It doesn't have to be a movie.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...but will you stay away from me for a while?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I bothering you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.83,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your existence isn't affecting my life in any way at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.62,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Kagami?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to talk to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.58,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me anything. We're friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great to know. Hey, what do you like to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... I can't take this anymore...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This "normal stuff" isn't for me after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never be "ordinary"...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.54,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've gone outside\Nif I knew this was going to happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here, It! Follow the clapping!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.75,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell must be Satchin! Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.62,0:14:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not fair, Sato!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat me, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to touch a place like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm the lowest rank of It!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.92,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you could defeat me,\Nthere would be the second and third It...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I smell Mama-lin!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.33,0:14:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama-lin! I'm the blindfolded It!\NI'm too strong without the blindfold!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You are Mama-lin, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.17,0:14:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say anything to me?\NDid I get the wrong person?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I can taste Mama-lin!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you crying, Mama-lin?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play, Mama-lin!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.88,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very dangerous when you're sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.67,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods around you play it smart\Nand distort the world for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.50,0:15:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, when you're sad, Tama's heart aches, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.33,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama's dumb and doesn't know what to do,\Nbut loves it when Mama-lin smiles!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.88,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.88,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.58,0:15:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore... I'm old.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.96,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun, wasn't it? Let's play together again, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I feel like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tama.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to make friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask me such a thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have any.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.25,0:15:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought Big Sis Kagami and you were friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis excitedly told me she made a new friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.96,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me you practiced together during P.E.\Nand teamed up during English class and stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she always has the same face,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I could tell she was happy\Nwhen she was talking about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're always worried because we're gods.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.12,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We could Alter things and make anyone our friends\Njust by wishing. That's why it's scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I play with my friends\Nor hear them say that they love me,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.58,0:16:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be forcing them to say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.38,0:16:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mama-lin and Big Sis Kagami are both gods,\Nso it's not the result of an Alteration...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are real friends, so I'm envious!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama-lin, please take care of Big Sis Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.71,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be over soon. It'll be over\Nbefore the end of this semester.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.12,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.96,0:16:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something Big Sis Kagami has to deal with.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So be patient for her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Downloading the talisman machinegun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Inputting the psychic missiles.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting Fire Emperor Kagutsuchi's Protect to Level B!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excite Yata no Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uninstalling vulnerability factor and damaged functions.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Switching heart and emotions to Sleep mode.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.58,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yaoyorozu cater to the Supreme God,\Nhoping to be liked by her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, the Supreme God is me! This foolish me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.08,0:17:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all things, I wished I had friends\Nand chose Kagami of all people!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.50,0:17:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the other gods became jealous\Nand started attacking Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.12,0:17:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a puppet with no will...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.42,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,An automated machine that achieves\Nthe most optimal result in the best method available.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.96,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I came to have a family and maybe friends, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.67,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I become her friend,\Nthe entire world would attack Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what's coming at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind getting bloody\Nfor the sake of the normal and ordinary,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if that's what my friend wants!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.21,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason she told me we were friends only at school
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.21,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,must be because maintaining the peace\Nin the school was the utmost she could do!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.54,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gratitude wasn't what I wanted,\Nbut I was simply happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.75,0:18:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So before my friend starts worrying unnecessarily...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I should take care of it while it's still a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send anyone who crosses me to the other world!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.71,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of my... Friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making me so mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.58,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Isn't it too early to come to school?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.67,0:19:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Isn't it too late for you to stay in school?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a nap and overslept.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.04,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I saw you walking with your classmates.\NAre they your friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.33,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any such friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw them being possessed by evil gods,\Nso I took them away from them.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.83,0:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've been secretly living in the humans\Nin order to get close to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.46,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you would've been very excited\Nbecause you're immature.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.25,0:20:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would've been a major problem if\Nthe evil gods talked you into Altering the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were worried about me...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.33,0:20:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me? Are you seriously that dumb?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kagami...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be worried, but I'm already done\Ncleaning inside the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.92,0:20:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you make new friends in the future,\Nit's not a result of an Alteration.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.71,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So just relax and try to enjoy a fun school life...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.75,0:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kagami! I was such an idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your snot is going to get all over me! It's nasty!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk some sense into those gods!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.42,0:20:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll make sure that they'll never ever\Ndo anything to hurt you! So... So...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying, you moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're creeping me out, you pig!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.12,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be my friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.21,0:21:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kagami! I don't want you to be a demo!\NBe my friend for real!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasami...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a puppet.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.12,0:21:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With a cold, empty heart and\Nno functionality to shed tears...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.79,0:21:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still aspired to be ordinary and normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.38,0:21:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to become an ordinary girl,\Nwho can cry and laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.58,0:21:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If my wish could come true...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.58,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,God... I would've wished to become human...\NA foolish and weak yet warm human...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.25,0:21:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already warm, Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.42,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to become a human?\NWill I be able to become a friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.79,0:22:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you will! No, let's try to be that together!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.62,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.83,0:22:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawn... I'd like to apologize for the appearance\Nof the Sasami impostor in the last episode.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.54,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff members ate the person in question.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.88,0:22:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They ate her?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.79,0:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.96,0:22:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it happened because your laziness made it possible\Nfor an impostor to take over this segment.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.42,0:22:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want you to give it all you've got.\NI'll help you out a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's sing together, Kagami!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be able to do it alone,\Nbut with you I'm sure I can!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yawn... Stop being such a baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.54,0:22:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cheer you on from here, so I want you to\Ngo out there and do what you have to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.67,0:23:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I think that was pretty fun this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.33,0:23:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.71,0:23:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never do this again.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for Ganbaranai Quiz.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.58,0:23:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,First question! What kind of question\Nam I going to give you now?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.33,0:23:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hint!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.00,0:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very hard question that\Nno one in the world can answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.29,0:24:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tic, tic, tic, pong!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.21,0:24:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is whatever you're thinking right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.62,0:24:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Second question!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.71,0:24:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the answer to the question\Nyou just thought of?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.21,0:24:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, Episode 6,\N"My Parents are the Only People That I'm Troubling"
